data.description: Well maintained one level home in desirable neighborhood.  Laminate flooring and new carpet. A spacious eating area is located just off the kitchen. Large living/dining room with slider to the back patio. Wood fireplace in the living room is great for cozy nights. The huge fenced yard with irrigation system is perfect for entertaining. Along with ample parking in large driveway for multiple cars or RV. Includes Home Warranty.
